narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Grant writing; reviewing papers; familiarity with cutting-edge debates in environmental anthropology; working as a group!

narratives.question_text: How well did the knowledge, skills, and insights gained in this class align with your expectations?
comments: Very well. DoveLab is an extraordinary space. In addition to the instructor, peers also often have valuable things to say.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of the course and how could it be improved?
What advice would you give to a student considering taking this class?
comments: Bring your imagination, creativity and sincerity to the table. It will help your peers, and you, to grow.
